	<element name="Illusionist's Gloves" type="Magic Item" source="Laurence Stuff" id="ID_TOD_ITEM_ILLUSIONISTS_GLOVES">
		<description>
			<p><strong>Wondrous Item, uncommon (requires attunement)</strong></p>
			<p>While wearing these gloves, when you cast an illusion spell that has both verbal and somatic components, you can ignore the verbal component of the spell.</p>
			<p>This benefit applies only if the spell requires a somatic component. Material components are unaffected.</p>
		</description>
		<setters>
			<set name="category">ToD Items</set>
			<set name="type">ToD Item</set>
			<set name="slot">hands</set>
			<set name="rarity">Uncommon</set>
			<set name="attunement">true</set>
			<set name="cost">0</set>
			<set name="weight">0 lb.</set>
		</setters>
	</element>

